<HEADLINE>
`CHICAGO HOPE' CREATOR SWOOPS IN _ STAT _ TO SAVE CBS SERIES 
</HEADLINE>
 HOPE-AZR   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By DAVE WALKER  
 c.1999 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; EDITORS: THIS STORY IS EMBARGOED FOR SUNDAY, MAY16
</P>
