<P>
   &UR; `OF ALL THE EMBASSIES IN ALL THE CITIES...WE HAD TO HIT THAT
ONE' &LR;  &QC;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (ATTN: Commentary Editors) &LR;  &QC;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; By RUPERT CORNWELL, The Independent of London &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   LONDON _ To misquote Humphrey Bogart: ``Of all the embassies in
all the cities in all the world, we had to hit that one'' _ the
mission in Belgrade of China, the country, after Russia, whose
consent is most vital if a United Nations resolution imposing a
Kosovo settlement is to succeed... &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (NOTE: This article can stand in 725; total uncut is 950
words) &LR;  &QC;
</P>
