<P>
   ANTI-DEPRESSANTS - It's no secret how popular antidepressants
have become - adults are using them for everything from phobias, to
anxiety in social situations to true depression. And so are kids.
Increasingly, the drugs, which like most medicines have never been
tested on children, are being prescribed to treat childhood
depression and social problems (Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
