way for the quick insertion of a U.S.-led combat force into Kosovo
to help ethnic Albanians return to their homes after a peace
settlement is reached. He again apologizes for the mistaken bombing
of China's embassy in Belgrade in a telephone call to Chinese
President Jiang Zemin. The gesture is essential to avoid China's
veto of the peace force in the U.N. Security Council. By STEWART M.
POWELL.
</P>
