controversy over $3 billion in missing or unaccounted-for money in
Indian trust funds, Interior Secretary Bruce Babbitt unveils a new
$60 million computer accounting system. A report by the General
Accounting Office, Congress' key investigative arm, says the system
may not work. By MARK HELM.
