director; with Jet Li, Lau Ching Wan, Francoise C.J. Yip. Reviewed
by Lawrence Van Gelder.
</P>
<P>
   TV-JOAN-REVIEW (Undated) _ On CBS, ``Joan of Arc,'' a four-hour
mini-series. Reviewed by Ron Wertheimer.
