u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HEARST-NEWS-BUDGET-1S     05-14 1236
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HEARST-NEWS-BUDGET-1STLD-WRITETHRU-HNS </SLUG>
  
 Friday, May 14, 1999    
 Editors      The Hearst News Service will file the following for
Saturday and Sunday. If you have questions, please call Susie McBee
or Tim Spence at 202-298-6920.    (The ``HNS'' tag appears in all
