the Houston Rockets picked themselves up off the mat and turned
this into a real playoff series. But will the Rockets be able to
duplicate that sense of urgency in Game 4 on Saturday afternoon? By
JONATHN FEIGEN.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-BLINEBURY-COLUMN (Houston) _ Fran Blinebury column on backup
