<P>
   BBN-ASTROS (Houston) _ The Houston Astros have won three
straight and 13 of their past 16 as they head into a three-game
weekend series against the San Francisco Giants in a battle of
first-place teams. By CARLTON THOMPSON
</P>
<P>
