   RUSSIA-POLITICS (Moscow) _ Chaos in Parliament during the
Yeltsin impeachment hearings; a vote is expected on Saturday.
Sergei Stepashin, the prime minister-designate, says he will keep
most of current Cabinet and will continue the course of Yevgeny
Primakov, the outgoing prime minister. By Celestine Bohlen.
</P>
