   (NYT42) NEW YORK -- May 14, 1999 -- BKN-KNICKS-HEAT-2, 5-14 --
Miami's Alonzo Mourning and Tim Hardaway defending New York's
Patrick Ewing on Friday night during game 4 of the first round
playoff series between the Knicks and the Heat. A New York victory
will propell the Knicks into the second round of the playoffs.
(Chang W. Lee/New York Times Photo)
